{
  "id": "5ad929045fdf010014a750df",
  "title": "経験と教育",
  "created": 1524181459,
  "updated": 1524276918,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ad929045fdf010014a750df",
      "text": "経験と教育",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181459,
      "updated": 1524181465
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad929daaff09e0000d52ebb",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/66b29dddb5a7d69663ad155f37ac1f2c]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181467,
      "updated": 1524181467
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad929d8aff09e0000d52eba",
      "text": "\t[経験]と[教育]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181465,
      "updated": 1524181493
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad929f2aff09e0000d52edb",
      "text": " [ジョン・デューイ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181490,
      "updated": 1524181520
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad92a11aff09e0000d52edd",
      "text": "\t[Amazon https://amzn.to/2qJp8PA]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181521,
      "updated": 1524181609
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad92a11aff09e0000d52ede",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181521,
      "updated": 1524181521
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad92a0caff09e0000d52edc",
      "text": "\t僕はジョン・デューイという名前を[プラグマティズム]の文脈で先に目にしていたので、ここで出てきたことが意外だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181517,
      "updated": 1524181581
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada997daff09e00006958a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275582,
      "updated": 1524275582
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad92b70aff09e00004459d1",
      "text": "\t1章 [伝統的教育] 対 [進歩主義教育]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524181872,
      "updated": 1524275614
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9a87aff09e00006958ad",
      "text": " \t人間は極端な対立で物事を考えがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275847,
      "updated": 1524275864
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9c21aff09e00006958ae",
      "text": "  伝統的教育：子供が現に持っている能力と無関係に、おとなの行動基準と教材と方法を[押し付け]る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276257,
      "updated": 1524276866
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada999faff09e00006958a5",
      "text": " 2章 [経験]についての理論の必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275615,
      "updated": 1524276860
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9c78aff09e00006958af",
      "text": " \t伝統的教育を否定するなら、経験についての理論が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276344,
      "updated": 1524276373
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada99aaaff09e00006958a6",
      "text": " 3章 経験の基準",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275626,
      "updated": 1524275634
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9ca4aff09e00006958b0",
      "text": " \t教育が経験を基礎にして知的に導かれ処理されるためには経験の理論の形成が必要、と述べて来た",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276388,
      "updated": 1524276419
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9cc2aff09e00006958b2",
      "text": "  次に、教育的に価値のある経験とそうでない経験の間を識別する基準が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276419,
      "updated": 1524276456
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9d1aaff09e00006958b3",
      "text": "  基準",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276506,
      "updated": 1524276508
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9d1caff09e00006958b4",
      "text": "  \t経験の[連続性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276508,
      "updated": 1524276876
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9d1eaff09e00006958b5",
      "text": "   [相互作用]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276511,
      "updated": 1524276878
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9cbaaff09e00006958b1",
      "text": " 4章 社会的統制",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276410,
      "updated": 1524276452
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada9dc8aff09e00006958b6",
      "text": " \t連続性と相互作用という2つの原理がどう現実の問題に関わってくるか論じるために、古くからの問題である「個人の自由と社会的統制」の問題を議論しよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524276680,
      "updated": 1524276737
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada99b6aff09e00006958a8",
      "text": " 5章 [自由の本性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275639,
      "updated": 1524276918
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada99bcaff09e00006958a9",
      "text": " 6章 [目的の意味]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275645,
      "updated": 1524276915
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada99c5aff09e00006958aa",
      "text": " 7章 教材の進歩主義的組織化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275653,
      "updated": 1524275663
    },
    {
      "id": "5ada99ceaff09e00006958ab",
      "text": " 8章 経験-教育の手段と目的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524275663,
      "updated": 1524275674
    },
